/* ------------------------------------------------------------
 * COLOURS
 * ------------------------------------------------------------
/* ------------------------------------------------------------
 * Matrix blue 				 : #105080
 * Matrix Orange 			 : #C60
 * Slitherine Green 	 : #6D9334
 * Background 				 : #F6F6F6 (faded gray)
 * 										 : #E7EDF2 (faded blue)
 * 										 : #DAE1D0 (faded green)
 * 										 : #EFECE9 (faded orange)
 * Baseline Text 			 : #333
 * Heading 2 					 : #666
 * Heading 3 					 : #105080 (background - Matrix)
